/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PV_GetLastValuationGiftAddition                      
** Short Desc: A data extract from GiftWrap, which gives gifts enetered in Giftwrap application     
**  for the specified ValuationID.          
** Full Description: A data extract from GiftWrap, which gives gifts enetered in Giftwrap application     
**  for the specified ValuationID.      
**                              
** Input Arguments:   	@EventID INT
**	,@ReturnStatus INT  OUTPUT
**	,@ErrorDesc VARCHAR(8000) OUTPUT             
** Sample Call     
        
 EXEC USP_PV_GetLastValuationGiftAddition @ValuationXML = '<ValuationCollection>    
      <InsertList>    
      <Valuation ValuationID="6" />    
      </InsertList>    
      </ValuationCollection>' 

**             
